{"tid":537324,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(魔性）A山現身曼徹斯特！淫魔準備做紅魔","createTime":"2018-01-22T15:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T16:51:22.000Z","uid":3806,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0784559f9ebe25413c83d070e284ed454ebba59f","tid":537324,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180121/photo/bkn-20180121222816978-0121_00882_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180121222816978-0121_00882_001_01p.jpg&h=1d62c0d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿仙奴前鋒阿歷斯山齊士，周日畀人踢爆背住女友偷食女學生，未做紅魔先做淫魔。不過，呢宗醜聞應該阻止唔到呢件淫魔加入紅魔大家庭，當地時間下晝2點畀人影到佢現身曼市，準備去曼聯訓練基地接受體測，極有可能周一正式公布加盟。 <br />\n<br />\n淫山中午畀人影到，到達紅魔基地卡靈頓接受體檢。據英國傳媒報道，呢位智利球星將會同曼聯簽約4年，周薪達50萬鎊，成為紅魔最高薪淫魔...唔係，球星至啱。英媒話紅魔最快周一宣布A山加盟，魔迷記得留意喇！"},{"pid":"b33f920b50b92194664943a75f2e8590e8f59941","tid":537324,"uid":3806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f557706936cb868d50b97e14360ff172b503340","tid":537324,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:05:49.000Z","msg":"麻友is g"},{"pid":"bcb62aaa88c12d4d1e68ddc8fd9ace7262a9aa3e","tid":537324,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:06:52.000Z","msg":"叻仔"},{"pid":"ff14f33495f2c52f4461db130f1fde8c32b52617","tid":537324,"uid":62343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"魔性"},{"pid":"636bec531042f89408068d53cbc2f66250129a7b","tid":537324,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f557706936cb868d50b97e14360ff172b503340","tid":537324,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:05:49.000Z","msg":"麻友is g"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i